text: Erik Harling (11 May 1910 - 16 November 1978) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1978 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm Category:Male breaststroke swimmers
